==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Despecificate
<hw>De`spe*cif"i*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>de-</ets> (intens.) + <ets>specificate</ets>.]</ety> <def>To
discriminate; to separate according to specific signification or
qualities; to specificate; to desynonymize.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Inaptitude and ineptitude have been usefully
<qex>despecificated</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Fitzed. Hall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Despecification</ent>⟦br⟧
